<b>Leicester Caribbean Carnival</b> is an annual event, held in early August in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../155/51155.xml">
Leicester</link></village>
, <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../316/9316.xml">
England</link></country>
.<p>

<image location="right" width="150px" src="Leicester_Caribbean_carnival.jpg" type="thumb">
<caption>

The carnival procession on London Road, 2004
</caption>
</image>
</p>

<p>

The community-organised <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../483/38483.xml">
carnival</link> has been held annually since <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../846/34846.xml">
1985</link> (except <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../164/36164.xml">
2006</link>) on the first Saturday in August, with a parade around the city of Leicester (usually taking in the city centre and the suburb of <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../477/2466477.xml">
Highfields</link>), culminating in an event on <region wordnetid="108630985" confidence="0.8">
<triumphal_arch wordnetid="104486054" confidence="0.8">
<structure wordnetid="104341686" confidence="0.8">
<artifact wordnetid="100021939" confidence="0.8">
<memorial wordnetid="103743902" confidence="0.8">
<park wordnetid="108615149" confidence="0.8">
<arch wordnetid="102733524" confidence="0.8">
<location wordnetid="100027167" confidence="0.8">
<tract wordnetid="108673395" confidence="0.8">
<geographical_area wordnetid="108574314" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../418/394418.xml">
Victoria Park</link></geographical_area>
</tract>
</location>
</arch>
</park>
</memorial>
</artifact>
</structure>
</triumphal_arch>
</region>
.  The parade is usually preceded by a week of cultural events.  It is the second-largest Caribbean carnival in the UK, after the <fundamental_quantity wordnetid="113575869" confidence="0.8">
<time_period wordnetid="115113229" confidence="0.8">
<event wordnetid="100029378" confidence="0.8">
<festival wordnetid="115162388" confidence="0.8">
<psychological_feature wordnetid="100023100" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../103/241103.xml">
Notting Hill Carnival</link></psychological_feature>
</festival>
</event>
</time_period>
</fundamental_quantity>
.</p>
<p>

The event didn't take place in 2006, due to a lack of funds, returning in 2007 <weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/leicester/content/articles/2006/05/17/caribbean_carnival_returns_feature.shtml">
http://www.bbc.co.uk/leicester/content/articles/2006/05/17/caribbean_carnival_returns_feature.shtml</weblink>.</p>

